		<h2>The University of Memphis</h2>
		<p>The University of Memphis is also called as UofM, is an American public research university. Founded in 1912, the university has an enrollment of more than 22,000 students. A faculty of approximately 930 professors serves about 17,000 undergraduate and 4,000 graduate students.</p>
		
		
		
		<h2>University Appointment Manager</h2>
		<p>This project is a web based application that finds an easy way for a student to schedule an appointment with the Professor or Employee in the Campus with the UofM mail within a single click. Students can access the Professors or Employee of different departments and can Schedule an appointment with them with the date, time and reason for appointment. Submitting an appointment will generate an automated email to the Professor or Employee stating the date, time and reason for the appointment. The Professor or Employee will inturn reply to the Student about the confirmation of the Scheduled appointment. </p>


